<div class="container-fluid image-background" id="about-1">
  <div class="image-overlay d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
    <h1 class="section-header exo white text-center no-margin">Who is Euro Bike Tours?</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container about-container">
  <div class="row no-gutters">
    <div class="col-12">
      <h1 class="page-header exo blue text-left no-margin">We specialise in crafting memorable travel experiences across Europe.</h1>
      <div class="underline"></div>
      <h2 class="sub-header kanit-3 mb3">We were founded in 2018, after a group of travel addicts and cycling enthusiasts noticed the lack of options for organised, multi-destination cycle travel.</h2>
      <p class="default-text kanit-3">Our aim is to make cycle tours accessible to all, whatever your ability, fitness level, or budget. We believe that travelling is as much about the journey as the destination, and there is no better way to experience the wonders of Europe than on two wheels.</p>
      <p class="default-text kanit-3">The freedom is unparalleled, and the excitement ever-present. We are passionate about what we do, and we hope you will take the next step on your travelling adventures with us!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid image-background" id="about-2">
  <div class="image-overlay d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
    <h1 class="section-header exo white text-center no-margin">Why should I use Euro Bike Tours?</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container about-container">
  <div class="row no-gutters">
    <div class="col-12">
      <h1 class="page-header exo blue text-left no-margin">We've been around the block, so we know a thing or two about organising a cycling trip...</h1>
      <div class="underline"></div>
      <h2 class="sub-header kanit-3 mb3">From the rolling Tuscan hills to the windswept flats of the Netherlands, we pride ourselves on our ability to create just about any imaginable itinerary.</h2>
      <p class="default-text kanit-3">Our team has extensive experience of cycling on the continent. If you book a tour with us, you won't find yourself at the roadside with a flat tyre and a soaking wet map written in a foreign language. You will receive a comprehensive pre-tour package, with guidance on everything from local customs, to cycling etiquette, and even the best coffee stops along the way!</p>
      <p class="default-text kanit-3">After many years of cycling around Europe, we established a vast network of friends and travel buddies who in turn became our trusted business partners. We have links with local bike shops, cafes, and accommodation, so you will never be too far away from a friendly face.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid image-background" id="about-3">
  <div class="image-overlay d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
    <h1 class="section-header exo white text-center no-margin">Should I Choose Guided or Self Guided?</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container about-container">
  <div class="row no-gutters mb3">
    <div class="col-12">
      <h1 class="page-header exo blue text-left no-margin">Freedom and Flexibility vs. Structure and Security</h1>
      <div class="underline"></div>
      <h2 class="sub-header kanit-3 mb3">This depends entirely on the level of flexibility you desire on your trip.</h2>
      <p class="default-text kanit-3">Choosing a guided tour is the best way to ensure that you see all of the main sights on your route. Our guides are experts on local knowledge, and they all speak at least one foreign language to an intermediate level. You can rest assured that everything is taken care of; all you need to bring is your energy!</p>
      <p class="default-text kanit-3">A self guided tour is the best way to get the most out of your trip on your own terms. Primarily, you won't have to stick to a strict schedule, meaning you can spend as much or as little time as you like in different places. Feel free to go back to that quirky little cafe you spotted yesterday; nobody is stopping you!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-6 card-col">
      <div class="card h-100">
        <div class="card-image" id="card-image-1">
          <div class="image-overlay d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
            <h2 class="card-title kanit-3 white text-center">Guided</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text kanit-3">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
            See all of the main sights on your itinerary, without worrying about navigation
          </p>
          <p class="card-text kanit-3">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
            Expert guides with in-depth local knowledge, and first-aid training
          </p>
          <p class="card-text kanit-3">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
            A friendly face who is on hand at all times to deal with your queries
          </p>
          <p class="card-text kanit-3">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
            Peace of mind, so you can leave the planning to us and focus on enjoying your travels
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-6 card-col">
      <div class="card h-100">
        <div class="card-image" id="card-image-2">
          <div class="image-overlay d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
            <h2 class="card-title kanit-3 white text-center">Self Guided</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="card-text kanit-3">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
            Choose where you want to go, when you want to go, and how long you want to spend there
          </p>
          <p class="card-text kanit-3">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
            A more 'authentic' experience, for those more adventurous
          </p>
          <p class="card-text kanit-3">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
            Choose which route you want to take: long and scenic, or short and sweet
          </p>
          <p class="card-text kanit-3">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
            Fully immerse yourself in the local environment
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid image-background" id="about-4">
  <div class="image-overlay d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
    <h1 class="section-header exo white text-center no-margin">Private or Group?</h1>
  </div>
</div>



